  "instructions": [
    "Preheat a medium skillet over medium heat.",
    "Brush each slice of bread with olive oil and toast until golden brown on both sides.",
    "In a small bowl, whisk together tahini, date syrup, lemon juice, water, ground cardamom, and a pinch of salt until smooth.",
    "Spread the tahini mixture evenly over the toasted bread slices.",
    "Sprinkle toasted almonds, sumac, lemon zest, and a pinch of sea salt over the sauce.",
    "Drizzle with a few drops of rose water for aroma.",
    "Gently press the toppings to adhere and allow the flavors to settle for 2 minutes.",
    "Slice the toast into bite‑sized pieces and serve immediately."
  ],
